This folder documents the local Kafka demo users used by the EventSmartKafka validation setup.

## Canonical Demo User

```text
username: sdia
password: SDIABRASIL
```

This is the only canonical user kept in the public local Kafka demo.

Do not reuse this password in any real environment.

## Authentication Coverage

The same demo user is used for:

| Listener | Port | Security |
|---|---:|---|
| `SASLEXT` | `19102` | SASL_PLAINTEXT |
| `SASLSSLEXT` | `19103` | SASL_SSL |

Supported mechanisms in the local demo:

```text
PLAIN
SCRAM-SHA-256
SCRAM-SHA-512
```

The reset/start script creates the SCRAM credentials for the user `sdia` automatically.
